<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA77">
<l>uraikkilōr cuṟṟattā ruṟṟāreṉ ṟārē</l>
<l>yiraikkuṅ kaṭaṟkiṭanta ventā yuraippellā</l>
<l>niṉṉaṉṟi maṟṟilēṉ kaṇṭā yeṉatuyirkkōr</l>
<l>colnaṉṟi yākun tuṇai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When talking about it, who are those that could be said to have kinsmen,</l>
<l>my father who lies on the roaring ocean? In all the sayings</l>
<l>I am without any other but you as a support that is</l>
<l>the benefit of a word for my life.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
